    "en": {
      "title": "Instruction regarding fuel supply",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "District Secretaries have been instructed to maintain proper control and management of fuel distribution activities.",
        "It is mentioned that these instructions have been issued by the Ministry of State Administration, Home Affairs, Provincial Councils and Local Government.",
        "The District Secretaries have also been notified to resolve the problematic situations in the fuel distribution scheme nationwide with proper coordination of the concerned departments. (a)"
      ],
